Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.03,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\frx1\fs50\c&H6A7277&\pos(696.667,278.667)\b1\frz295.6}Lâu đài Mộ{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.03,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fry-5\frx1\fax-0.01\blur0.5\fs25\c&H717A81&\b1\frz293.2\pos(632.429,300.143)}Cuộc chạy trốn khỏi lâu đài xác sống!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.03,sign1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fry-5\frx1\fax-0.01\blur0.5\fs25\c&H717A81&\b1\frz293.2\pos(619.428,466.286)}Kanda Sorata
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cậu mới làm lại cái khác à?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ừ.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.03,0:16:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,À, phải rồi, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sau này có gì giúp tớ nhé?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giúp gì?
